articles.title: 4 standout Arsenal players from emphatic Champions League victory over Lens - Pain In The Arsenal
articles.description: 4 standout performers from Arsenal's demolition of Lens in the Champions League.
articles.content:
Arsenal ran riot against RC Lens at the Emirates, scoring a whopping five first-half goals. A late Jorginho penalty secured a 6-0 win, ensuring that the Gunners will finish top of Group B.
